quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  29,31,"Tuma nde Imminaa…ďe Amen …ďen addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo ngon, …ďe mb"i: "Minen, ko men halkoo…ďee yim…ďe ndee saare. Tawde pellet, yim…ďe mayre laatike too√Īoo…ďe"."
  29,32,"O maaki: "Kono Luutu no ton!" ∆Āe mbi'i: "Ko minen …ďuri anndude fii won'…ďe ton. Ko ma men da…óndu mo, kaŇčko e yim…ďe makko …ďen, si wonaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e helketee…ďe …ďeen"."
  29,33,"Tum nde imminaa…ďe Amen …ďen keewtunoo ka Luutu, o sa…ótiraa fii ma…ď…ďe, …ďernde makko …ďi…ótorii fii ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe mbi'i: "Wota a hul, wota a suno. Ko men da…óndoo…ďe ma an e …ďeynguure maa nde, si wonaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e halkaa…ďe …ďen."
  29,34,"Ko moen njippinoo…ďe lepte e yim…ďe ndee saare, immorde ka kammu, sabu ko …ďe yaltunoo e …óoftaare kon"."
  29,35,"GooŇč…óii Min ngaccii e nden (saare), Ma'ande …ďanngunde, wonan'de yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe …ďeen."
  29,36,"(Min nuli) kadi e Madyana, musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on, Shu'aybu. O maaki: "Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla, jortoron √Ďalannde sakkitiinde nden, wota woniri e leydi ndin, bonnoo…ďe"."
  29,37,"Kono …ďe njeddi i mo. Dillannde nden nanngi …ďe, …ďe wa…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe, ko …ďe jiccii…ďe-maayi."
  29,38,"(Meon kalki) kadi Aadi'en, e Saamuda'en. GooŇč…óii caambbeje ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďannganii on. Seytaane cu…óinani …ďe, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, ndu sakkii …ďe e laawol ngol; tawi le, ko …ďe reentunoo…ďe."